{"tid":214011,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"羅志祥宣佈退出facebook","createTime":"2017-04-23T13:24:46.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-24T00:19:45.000Z","uid":25345,"like":4,"dislike":154,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1c3bb5dd7c167bcada595ded7ac55fdab4702999","tid":214011,"uid":25345,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:24:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/IjqL5l2ESFpKVIU5_ctXyg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw/http://media.zenfs.com/zh-Hant-HK/homerun/entertainment.nownews.hk/f5db5fe85764079350f04a7c43b3779e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FIjqL5l2ESFpKVIU5_ctXyg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9ODAw%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-Hant-HK%2Fhomerun%2Fentertainment.nownews.hk%2Ff5db5fe85764079350f04a7c43b3779e&h=3f885891&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「亞洲舞王」羅志祥日前在臉書透露因為遇到一些「突發情況」，而受到很大的打擊與影響，所以宣布將不再使用Facebook，並謝謝粉絲一直以來的陪伴。更於文末宣布退出原因，讓不少粉絲在看完全文後都表示相當傻眼！<br />\n<br />\n羅志祥在臉書先是向粉絲道歉，表示受了一些打擊與影響，更說「不打算玩Facebook了，和大家正式道個別吧！」並淚謝粉絲的支持與鼓勵，坦言「很喜歡看你們給我的留言，還有很喜歡跟你們互動。」羅志祥隨後透露退出原因是「手機沒電！」並調皮笑說「我要去充下電，等下充滿了，我就回來了&hellip;&hellip;」瞬間讓粉絲又好氣又好笑！<br />\n<br />\n不少粉絲在看羅志祥前面的「退出宣言」都相當緊張，而後看到退出原因是「沒電」則猛翻白眼。有網友則笑說：「我好想打你」、「棍子在哪裡？」、「要不要送你行動電源？」"},{"pid":"6f5eec30cbcac5d0ef873b4565b166648291be7c","tid":214011,"uid":17677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:25:28.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"b464ca468d50157da4e85de3b8993ab711e556b7","tid":214011,"uid":102661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:27:02.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"e7b25f8ccab092636c3ddfc73a0796b07a3fc79f","tid":214011,"uid":38737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:28:56.000Z","msg":"退出娛樂圈就話姐"},{"pid":"0738b3802c7488519e915efdbfbe00ae2c9491a6","tid":214011,"uid":60716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T13:29:27.000Z","msg":"wfc"},{"pid":"ba78a868ffd1411288044139aac0f8eb7b731c07",